      </seglistitem>
    </segmentedlist>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de DejaGNU</title>

    <para>The upstream recommends building DejaGNU in a dedicated build directory:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="pre">mkdir -v build
cd       build</userinput></screen>

    <para>Préparez DejaGNU à la compilation&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="configure">../configure --prefix=/usr
makeinfo --html --no-split -o doc/dejagnu.html ../doc/dejagnu.texi
makeinfo --plaintext       -o doc/dejagnu.txt  ../doc/dejagnu.texi</userinput></screen>

    <para>Construisez et installez le paquet&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="install">make install
install -v -dm755  /usr/share/doc/dejagnu-&dejagnu-version;
install -v -m644   doc/dejagnu.{html,txt} /usr/share/doc/dejagnu-&dejagnu-version;</userinput></screen>

    <para>Pour tester les résultats, lancez&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="test">make check</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>


